Classes in com.google.ase.jsonrpc used by com.google.ase.facade
Rpc
          The Rpc annotation is used to annotate server-side implementations of RPCs.
RpcDefaultBoolean
          This annotation marks an Integer parameter as optional and supplies a default value.
RpcDefaultInteger
          This annotation marks an Integer parameter as optional and supplies a default value.
RpcDefaultString
          This annotation marks an String parameter as optional and supplies a default value.
RpcOptionalString
          This annotation marks an String parameter as optional (a value of null will be passed in if the string is not defined).
RpcParameter
          An annotation that is used to document the parameters of an RPC.
